<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8" standalone="no"?><?Xpress productLine="ncc-clause" ?><clause xmlns:xt="urn:xpressauthor:trackchanges" author="Kieran O'Donnell" dateTime="2021-02-26T14:21:14" id="_5de41733-d324-4bfd-be75-e3e3964eda78" outputclass="ncc-clause" type="insert"><meta><facet building="Class 2"/><facet building="Class 3"/><facet building="Class 4"/><facet building="Class 5"/><facet building="Class 6"/><facet building="Class 7a"/><facet building="Class 7b"/><facet building="Class 8"/><facet building="Class 9a"/><facet building="Class 9b"/><facet building="Class 9c"/><facet building="Class 10b"/><facet climate="Climate zone 8"/></meta><sptc>4.2.22</sptc><title id="_1e6af721-2be4-4520-941e-d710af1c2516">Recessed areas of slabs</title><archive-num>New for 2022</archive-num><subclause id="_938ffefb-7110-4dd0-9001-0d1325e01194" outputclass="subclause"><title id="_7c658a76-6cf3-4f44-acdc-488e4c53abcc">SubClause</title><num>1</num><p>Where a recess in a slab is provided, a thickening must be provided in accordance with one of the following:</p><ol outputclass="alpha"><li id="_8ca89579-935d-45da-a614-a00f39db2ace">For recess depths (d) less than or equal to half the nominal slab thickness (see <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/8bd50c59-637c-4a79-8565-09cd674ed7ed/4692_0.20.0.xml#_0beb21d4-5560-45fa-ae48-667892cfe6a1" id="_24ae4009-1fad-42ee-9848-b43858efbcae" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="image-reference">Figure 4.2.22a</xref>)—<ol><li>a thickening must be provided not less than 400 mm measured horizontally from the inside face of each side of the recess (L); and</li><li>the reinforcing mesh must—<ol><li>be bent to accommodate the recess (see <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/8bd50c59-637c-4a79-8565-09cd674ed7ed/4692_0.20.0.xml#_0beb21d4-5560-45fa-ae48-667892cfe6a1" id="_0b0a95b1-1d30-43fa-9460-77c355899e96" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="image-reference">Figure 4.2.22a</xref>); or</li><li>be installed in accordance with (b)(i) and (ii).</li></ol></li></ol></li><li id="_369c969f-049c-4a05-8fa5-f0a4a522b1a7">For recess depths (d) greater than half the nominal slab thickness (see <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/8bd50c59-637c-4a79-8565-09cd674ed7ed/4693_0.17.0.xml#_5d825e21-cc09-44c6-b287-a7706090c8d0" id="_fd9259ab-2359-43a0-80bc-4f2eecdd546b" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="image-reference">Figure 4.2.22b</xref>)—<ol><li id="_ed6013aa-f54c-462a-a5fd-149f8762d679">top reinforcing mesh must overlap the bottom reinforcing mesh by not less than 400 mm; and</li><li>bottom reinforcing mesh must be two layers of SL72.</li></ol></li></ol></subclause><subclause id="_f863d84e-2416-4c80-9820-f3ca02685ca4" outputclass="subclause"><title id="_5246e936-3972-419f-a2ee-867b5a2d3f5f">SubClause</title><num>2</num><p>Concrete cover to reinforcing in (1)(a) and (b) must comply with <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/8bd50c59-637c-4a79-8565-09cd674ed7ed/1021_0.24.0.xml#_15ebc78c-0c6b-4a3e-a61d-87bce8479aab" id="_951f50cb-9d50-4758-ab94-e57ea7730847" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="subclause">4.2.11(5)</xref>.</p></subclause><subclause id="_d84e31c0-f733-4a0c-96f9-0860e4175ea0" outputclass="subclause"><title id="_8611f68a-9d9b-4e02-a103-d1ee2b370b6d">SubClause</title><num>3</num><p>Thickening required by (1) must be not less than the sum of recess depth (d) and the <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/8bd50c59-637c-4a79-8565-09cd674ed7ed/1432_4.0.0.xml#_af6fde9f-147d-4782-8b85-42044e80fd42" id="_c116a953-9451-4927-bc20-0d09432163d1" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="abcb-glossentry">required</xref> slab depth (D).</p></subclause><subclause id="_21f616e0-5030-4172-9877-7aed2b706a73" outputclass="subclause"><title id="_532f264f-9e6e-4a41-928e-30180101a6fc">SubClause</title><num>4</num><p><xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/8bd50c59-637c-4a79-8565-09cd674ed7ed/1432_4.0.0.xml#_af6fde9f-147d-4782-8b85-42044e80fd42" id="_f57b8b46-c32e-4b57-8212-abf4c631b437" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="abcb-glossentry">Required</xref> slab depth (D) must be provided below the recess.</p></subclause><image-reference author="Kieran O'Donnell" conref="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/8bd50c59-637c-4a79-8565-09cd674ed7ed/4692_0.20.0.xml" dateTime="2021-02-26T11:33:22" id="_0beb21d4-5560-45fa-ae48-667892cfe6a1" type="insert"><num/><title id="_9f55fcca-8cf6-4a2a-8854-b50353f59b90"/></image-reference><image-reference author="Kieran O'Donnell" conref="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/8bd50c59-637c-4a79-8565-09cd674ed7ed/4693_0.17.0.xml" dateTime="2021-02-26T11:33:57" id="_5d825e21-cc09-44c6-b287-a7706090c8d0" type="insert"><num/><title id="_7441180c-0c85-4298-8cf9-d4ea13a9f401"/></image-reference></clause>